creator: Video Mixer Video Editor
descriptionHtml:
Color Sketch Art Photo Editor
Color Sketch Art Photo Editor is an Application that can make your photo like a real sketch. User can make sketch of your photos easily by using This "Color Sketch Art Photo Editor" application.
Sketch Art Photo Editor app includes the best sketch feature to make beautiful sketch effects. Sketch Art Photo Editor let user create a wonderful picture art as same as pencil drawn.
By using Sketch Art Photo Editor application user can make the photos into black and white sketch first then added effects into photo.
Now, sketch art is totally free and amazing application to create colorful sketch of your photos very easily in few seconds. Sketching is an art that makes your photo into pencil sketch in black and white sketch but Sketch Art Photo Editor makes your photos into colorful sketch by using different photos or color effects.
Sketch Art Photo Editor has variety of bleeding pixels in various styles like Photoshop Shattering Effect. Photo Blending Effect is to focus on objects to make them the center of attraction! effects allows you to create amazing professional photos against a beautifully pixelated background.
User can make sketch by using sketch art app only select picture from gallery or camera first then this app converts the photo into sketch. Now select best photo blending effect and adjust seek-bar to create best sketch art effect
It is an amazing application to make pencil sketch of your photos easily in second's. You can make a real sketches of your photos using this application "Sketch Photo Art".
We have added to many sketch art styles background in this app you can select any one from them easily. Sketch Art Photo Editor allows user to create a wonderful picture art as same as pencil drawn.
Download this wonderful app and create best stunning photos.

App Feature of Sketch Art Photo Editor ::

Photo Sketch Art Editor ::
* Select a photo from gallery album & Crop it as you like.
* First, Convert your photos to sketch art.
* Now apply best hd photo blending background over your photos.
* We give your Different color Shades templates for any picture.
* Splash a different coloring on your pictures with vivid colors.
* Add text to photo, Change style, Change text Color, transparency, and add shadows.
* Add Lots of stylish sticker over photos easily.
* Simple touch gestures to rotate, re size, and delete any text & Sticker.
* Finally save and share your creative photos with friends and family.

Photo Lab Effect ::
* Select Your Best Photo from your album gallery.
* Adjust your photo in Final Canvas.
* Select Best & Unique Shattering Effect Mask that suit your photos.
* We give you 100+ Shattering mask effect.
* Change Background with unique color palette.
* Apply awesome photo filter over your stylish pics.
* Make your photo more beautiful by apply designing texture background over your photos.

Please email us if your device is not supported, we will try our best to support it.
